trans-unit.source: Interface that is used by the host infrastructure for property editing to handle sorting and filtering functionality.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnitt som brukes av verten-infrastruktur for egenskapen redigering til å håndtere sortering og filtrering funksjonaliteten.

trans-unit.source: It is used to determine whether a particular object should be filtered out.
trans-unit.target: Den brukes til å finne ut om en bestemt objekt skal filtreres.

trans-unit.source: Used to set a new <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter"></xref> on the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Brukes til å angi en ny <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter"> </xref> på den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Declaration of the event raised when a <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter"></xref> is changed through a call to <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget.ApplyFilter*>.
trans-unit.target: Deklarasjon av hendelsen aktiveres når en <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter"> </xref> endres via et kall til <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget.ApplyFilter*>.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget.ApplyFilter*>

trans-unit.source: Read-only property that returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter"></xref> is a match for the object.
trans-unit.target: Skrivebeskyttet egenskap som returnerer <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> hvis den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilter"> </xref> er et samsvar for objektet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the property filter matches the property filter target; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis egenskapsfilteret samsvarer med egenskapen filter måltype. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Used to determine whether this <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget"></xref> is a match for a particular <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilterPredicate"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Brukes til å bestemme om dette <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.IPropertyFilterTarget"> </xref> er et samsvar for en bestemt <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyFilterPredicate"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if it there is a match between a property filter target and a property filter predicate; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis det vises et samsvar mellom egenskapen filter mål og et egenskapen filterpredikat; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
